sentence:
Original sentence: "Police said in a statement at the time that they made the decision to end the search for Jacsun with a "heavy heart," but noted they couldn't pinpoint a location in the landfill "to a point that would make continuing the search reasonable."" 
 Translated sentence: "警方在当时的一份声明中表示，他们决定以“沉重的心情”结束对 Jacsun 的搜索，但指出他们无法确定垃圾填埋场的位置，“以至于继续搜索是合理的”。"

Original sentence: "Trump will likely veto the resolution, the sixth time he will have blocked congressional legislation as president. He already vetoed a measure to end the emergency declaration in March." 
 Translated sentence: "特 朗 普 可 能 会 否 决 该 决 议 ， 这 是 他 第 六 次 以 总 统 身 份 阻 止 国 会 立 法 ， 他 已 经 在 3 月 份 否 决 了 一 项 结 束 紧 急 声 明 的 措 施 。"

Original sentence: "The man arrived at work about 9.30am after failing to reply to several text messages and phone calls from colleagues." 
 Translated sentence: "该名男子未能回复同事的几条短信和电话，于上午9.30左右上班。"

Original sentence: "Are hopes for a nuclear-free world realistic?" 
 Translated sentence: "对一个无核世界的希望是现实的吗 ？"

Original sentence: "The California attorney general's office in March declined to issue state criminal charges after a nearly yearlong investigation. Attorney General Xavier Becerra said then evidence showed the officers had reason to believe their lives were in danger because he was advancing toward them holding what they thought was a gun. Investigators found only a cellphone." 
 Translated sentence: "3月,加利福尼亚总检察长办公室在经过近一年的调查后拒绝提出州刑事指控,当时,总检察长Xavier Becerra说,证据显示,警察有理由相信他们的生命有危险,因为他正朝着他们看着他们认为是枪的方向前进,调查人员只找到了手机。"

Original sentence: "He said he rejected the proposal because, "under sanctions and maximum pressure," it would have been impossible to predict the end result of any negotiations." 
 Translated sentence: "他说，他拒绝了这一提议，因为“在制裁和最大压力下”，不可能预测任何谈判的最终结果。"

Original sentence: "He added, "@leondame MURDERED the catwalk @maisonmargiela. Guess it's true what they say. There ain't nothin" like a DAME!"" 
 Translated sentence: "他补充道 ， “@ leondame MURDERED 的时装秀 @ misonmargiela. 猜他们说的是真的 ， 没有什么“ 像 DAME ！ ”"

Original sentence: "Earlier, Baloch's mother Anwar Mai told AFP she had hoped her son would be acquitted." 
 Translated sentence: "早些时候,巴洛克的母亲安瓦尔·马伊告诉菲律宾武装部队,她希望她的儿子被宣告无罪。"

Original sentence: ""My wife writes down the numbers for me during the drawing," Lancaster said. "When she handed me the paper, so I could check my ticket, I couldn't believe it. One of my lines matched five numbers and the other ones matched four numbers. I started shouting, 'I got it! I got it! I hit the lottery!'"" 
 Translated sentence: "′′我的妻子在画中为我写下了数字,"兰开斯特说. ′′当她把纸递给我, 所以我可以检查我的票, 我简直不敢相信. 我的一个台词匹配五个数字, 其他台词匹配四个数字. 我开始大喊我明白了! 我知道了! 我中奖了! ' ′′"

Original sentence: "Miller was one of several musicians whose deaths have been linked in recent years to a national wave of opioid abuse and overdoses." 
 Translated sentence: "米勒是近年来与全国阿片类药物滥用和过量使用有关的几位音乐家之一。"
